creator: Neabot Tech Co Limited
descriptionHtml:
Neabot is the application used to configure and control the Neabot robot vacuum.
With Neabot you can achieve the following functions.
- Scheduled cleaning: schedule a cleaning task and Neabot automatically cleans, empties its dustbin and charges after it finishes cleaning.
- Zone cleaning: after creating a map on the app, you can choose which rooms to be cleaned and adjust the suction power and water volume.
- Map management: easily set up rooms and no-go zones.
- Spot cleaning: Neabot cleans at the designated locations on the map.
- Consumables log: easy to keep track of consumables usage.
- Firmware upgrade: Neabot can have new features with a firmware upgrade.
- Dust collection management: customize the dust collection frequency to suit your home.
- Voice: More choices for languages and voices are constantly being updated.
descriptionShort: Neabot is the application used to configure and control the Neabot robot vacuum.
